text: Andrea Cano (born 18 May 1976) is an Italian football manager and former player. He played as a goalkeeper. He is currently a coach for goalkeepers at Padova. ==References== ==Other websites== * Profile at Legaserieb.it * Profile at Football.it Category:1976 births Category:Living people Category:Italian association football goalkeepers Category:Italian football managers Category:Footballers from Rome
